function colocaCartasEnZonas()

    local objectsInZone = zonaCanasta.getObjects()
    if #objectsInZone ~= 0 then
        local posicion = {}
        local rotation = {0,0,0}
        posicion.x = posicionZona.x
        posicion.y = posicionZona.y
        posicion.z = posicionZona.z -2.25
        for _, object in ipairs(objectsInZone) do
            local name = object.getName()
            if name ~= "" then
            else
                -- print("No name object found.")
            end
              object.setPosition(posicion)
              object.setRotation(rotation)
              -- object.setLock(true)
              posicion.z = posicion.z+0.75
              posicion.y = posicion.y+0.005
        end
        posicion.x = posicionZona.x
        posicion.y = posicionZona.y
        posicion.z = posicionZona.z -2.25
    end

    --Finally, we print the "closing" line.
    --The purpose of the first and last lines are decorative and for clarity
    -- print("[b]---------------------[/b]")
end
